interventions.interventions:
Head lice products are applied to the hair and massaged in. A single application is used.
GROUP 1: NeutraLice Lotion (containing Melaleuca Oil (Tea Tree Oil) 10% and Lavender Oil 1% - Key Pharmaceuticals Pty. Ltd.);
GROUP 2: NeutraLice Advance (a suffocating product containing benzyl alcohol, mineral oil, polysorbate 80, sorbitan monooleate, Carbopol 934 and triethanolamine Key Pharmaceuticals Pty. Ltd.)
